<div type="abstract"><head>Vermerk über Ausstellung eines Kredenzbriefs</head><p>Kredenzbrief für Hans Maurer an Herzog Heinrich XVI. von Bayern-Landshut wegen des Waffenstillstands bis Michaelstag mit Jobst von Abensberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="108v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_217_r2l20"><expan>Jt<ex>em</ex></expan> eın credecʒ an <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Payern . auf <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l21">ʒu werben als von des <expan>gütlıch<ex>en</ex></expan> ſteens <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ ſein gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l22"><expan>ʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> dem edeln <expan>H<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jobſten <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu <expan>Abemſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_217_r2l23">beſtellt hett auf <expan>Michahel<ex>is</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_217" id="108v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan> ein credecz an <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Payern auf
                            <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> zu werben als von des
                                <expan>gütlich<ex>en</ex></expan> steens
                            <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> daz sein gnade
                            <expan>zwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> dem edeln
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jobsten, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                                <expan>Abemsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        bestellt hett auf <app><note><q type="date"><expan>Michahel<ex>is</ex></expan> schierist</q>29.09.1415</note></app>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
